## Limitations

The findings are based on available online sources, which may not cover all aspects of government control comprehensively. The search was limited to English-language content, potentially excluding relevant perspectives from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the analysis is constrained by the publication dates of the sources, which may not reflect the most current developments in government control mechanisms.